{"pr_number": 456, "pr_title": "New documentation using Antora and @ConnectorAttribute", "pr_createdAt": "2020-03-20T12:43:53Z", "pr_url": "https://github.com/smallrye/smallrye-reactive-messaging/pull/456", "timeline": [{"oid": "5122b07d76777a949c58c8dfe466be8d50ccbe8b", "url": "https://github.com/smallrye/smallrye-reactive-messaging/commit/5122b07d76777a949c58c8dfe466be8d50ccbe8b", "message": "Implement @ConnectorAttribute support\n\nIt generates the class giving access to the configuration and the documentation files.", "committedDate": "2020-03-20T13:05:51Z", "type": "commit"}, {"oid": "915c2ef83bd96635c17410e330c8b8aa9518f958", "url": "https://github.com/smallrye/smallrye-reactive-messaging/commit/915c2ef83bd96635c17410e330c8b8aa9518f958", "message": "Display configuration table in the AMQP documentation", "committedDate": "2020-03-20T13:05:51Z", "type": "forcePushed"}, {"oid": "e8287fded122c397d4b9c790c65b92adf1677bae", "url": "https://github.com/smallrye/smallrye-reactive-messaging/commit/e8287fded122c397d4b9c790c65b92adf1677bae", "message": "Initial migration of the documentation to Antora.", "committedDate": "2020-03-20T13:09:36Z", "type": "commit"}, {"oid": "2de6b98e8743532a90b79d09ec3ca6f6a955bc28", "url": "https://github.com/smallrye/smallrye-reactive-messaging/commit/2de6b98e8743532a90b79d09ec3ca6f6a955bc28", "message": "Migrate HTTP Connector configuration to @ConnectorAttribute\n\nUpdate HTTP connector attributes based on the current documentation", "committedDate": "2020-03-20T13:09:36Z", "type": "commit"}, {"oid": "cd83c70196001f6901155019740a86d3bbdd98e3", "url": "https://github.com/smallrye/smallrye-reactive-messaging/commit/cd83c70196001f6901155019740a86d3bbdd98e3", "message": "Handle alias in the configuration classes\n\nRestructure the code to be more maintainable.", "committedDate": "2020-03-20T13:09:36Z", "type": "commit"}, {"oid": "063b475c984f7f634428f4da5ea1b86340be2644", "url": "https://github.com/smallrye/smallrye-reactive-messaging/commit/063b475c984f7f634428f4da5ea1b86340be2644", "message": "Migrate the AMQP connector to use the generated Configuration classes", "committedDate": "2020-03-20T13:09:36Z", "type": "commit"}, {"oid": "1703619f8223ffa8e49c1fc2db357d1295be7d8f", "url": "https://github.com/smallrye/smallrye-reactive-messaging/commit/1703619f8223ffa8e49c1fc2db357d1295be7d8f", "message": "Improve the table layout listing the connector attribute", "committedDate": "2020-03-20T13:09:36Z", "type": "commit"}, {"oid": "90f8f66ce798d788fb70ced3c70d4685e85f551e", "url": "https://github.com/smallrye/smallrye-reactive-messaging/commit/90f8f66ce798d788fb70ced3c70d4685e85f551e", "message": "Display configuration table in the AMQP documentation", "committedDate": "2020-03-20T13:09:36Z", "type": "commit"}, {"oid": "90f8f66ce798d788fb70ced3c70d4685e85f551e", "url": "https://github.com/smallrye/smallrye-reactive-messaging/commit/90f8f66ce798d788fb70ced3c70d4685e85f551e", "message": "Display configuration table in the AMQP documentation", "committedDate": "2020-03-20T13:09:36Z", "type": "forcePushed"}, {"id": "MDI0OlB1bGxSZXF1ZXN0UmV2aWV3Q29tbWVudDM5NTY0MTcxNA==", "url": "https://github.com/smallrye/smallrye-reactive-messaging/pull/456#discussion_r395641714", "bodyText": "Antora needs to run from a git repo, but if you want to spare yourself the need to do git init you can change this to\ncontent:\n    sources:\n        - url: ../../..\n          start_path: documentation/target/antora\n          branches: HEAD                    \n\nand it will reuse the existing git repo", "author": "jmartisk", "createdAt": "2020-03-20T13:39:25Z", "path": "documentation/src/main/antora/antora-playbook.yml", "diffHunk": "@@ -0,0 +1,18 @@\n+# partial playbook just for this project to be able to compile documentation without pushing it to GitHub\n+# usage: antora generate antora-playbook.yml\n+site:\n+    title: SmallRye Reactive Messaging Documentation\n+    start_page: smallrye-reactive-messaging::index.adoc\n+content:\n+    sources:\n+        - url: ./", "originalCommit": "90f8f66ce798d788fb70ced3c70d4685e85f551e", "replyToReviewId": null, "replies": null, "type": "inlineReview"}, {"oid": "c6828b4e6426d817a569946afdd6eaef1809f8ac", "url": "https://github.com/smallrye/smallrye-reactive-messaging/commit/c6828b4e6426d817a569946afdd6eaef1809f8ac", "message": "Migrate the SNS connector to connector attribute\n\nAlso cleanup the configuration and the code.", "committedDate": "2020-03-21T10:47:04Z", "type": "commit"}, {"oid": "e958790799feccb5490576a71a5f9acb10949eb8", "url": "https://github.com/smallrye/smallrye-reactive-messaging/commit/e958790799feccb5490576a71a5f9acb10949eb8", "message": "Add support for connector having a single ConnectorAttribute", "committedDate": "2020-03-21T14:45:23Z", "type": "commit"}, {"oid": "7d3d48917abdd4977fe3dc1ec9ebe7a5a7813aeb", "url": "https://github.com/smallrye/smallrye-reactive-messaging/commit/7d3d48917abdd4977fe3dc1ec9ebe7a5a7813aeb", "message": "Switch the Camel connector to ConnectorAttribute.", "committedDate": "2020-03-21T14:51:24Z", "type": "commit"}, {"oid": "60f3f4b82191289580f430c62e4acc29c1034f8f", "url": "https://github.com/smallrye/smallrye-reactive-messaging/commit/60f3f4b82191289580f430c62e4acc29c1034f8f", "message": "Rework the Antora support", "committedDate": "2020-03-21T16:01:13Z", "type": "commit"}, {"id": "MDI0OlB1bGxSZXF1ZXN0UmV2aWV3Q29tbWVudDM5NjIzNTM0Ng==", "url": "https://github.com/smallrye/smallrye-reactive-messaging/pull/456#discussion_r396235346", "bodyText": "Does this need to be a variable? I mean, even if your project.version is for example 1.3.5-SNAPSHOT, the \"documentation version\" will probably be 1.3 (we will not produce a different doc version for each micro release or so)\nWhat I was expecting to do with this is that we simply put in the major.minor version here and update it manually once in a while (which will basically be only when you create a new branch targeting a different minor version, so not very often)", "author": "jmartisk", "createdAt": "2020-03-23T06:33:24Z", "path": "documentation/src/main/doc/antora.yml", "diffHunk": "@@ -0,0 +1,5 @@\n+name: smallrye-reactive-messaging\n+title: SmallRye Reactive Messaging\n+version: ${project.version}", "originalCommit": "60f3f4b82191289580f430c62e4acc29c1034f8f", "replyToReviewId": null, "replies": [{"id": "MDI0OlB1bGxSZXF1ZXN0UmV2aWV3Q29tbWVudDM5NjIzODY2Mg==", "url": "https://github.com/smallrye/smallrye-reactive-messaging/pull/456#discussion_r396238662", "bodyText": "I caught it yesterday. I missed it.\nThe issue is that it avoids the release process automation without adding a commit in the process. Adding a commit is not impossible, just tricky as I will rely on regexp and replacement.\nNote that most of the time we are releasing minor, so it would require an increment every time (more or less).", "author": "cescoffier", "createdAt": "2020-03-23T06:45:36Z", "replyToReviewId": "MDI0OlB1bGxSZXF1ZXN0UmV2aWV3Q29tbWVudDM5NjIzNTM0Ng=="}, {"id": "MDI0OlB1bGxSZXF1ZXN0UmV2aWV3Q29tbWVudDM5Njk0MDM4Ng==", "url": "https://github.com/smallrye/smallrye-reactive-messaging/pull/456#discussion_r396940386", "bodyText": "I found a way to extract this in Maven.", "author": "cescoffier", "createdAt": "2020-03-24T07:12:56Z", "replyToReviewId": "MDI0OlB1bGxSZXF1ZXN0UmV2aWV3Q29tbWVudDM5NjIzNTM0Ng=="}], "type": "inlineReview"}, {"oid": "b7b1ed40407c27cac0436a620302aca9a58b5ac7", "url": "https://github.com/smallrye/smallrye-reactive-messaging/commit/b7b1ed40407c27cac0436a620302aca9a58b5ac7", "message": "Reimplement the Antora build process.", "committedDate": "2020-03-23T13:23:12Z", "type": "commit"}, {"oid": "7590c9d2613be15490e2a979e1d56626e819f56e", "url": "https://github.com/smallrye/smallrye-reactive-messaging/commit/7590c9d2613be15490e2a979e1d56626e819f56e", "message": "Rewrite the concept documentation", "committedDate": "2020-03-23T13:24:29Z", "type": "commit"}, {"oid": "61d512bbf533d0efdb0d451cc96ddfcdf4c16580", "url": "https://github